Modifications.Value: Causes a target enemy unit to be bound to the ground so that it cannot move for <A07J,Dur1> seconds. Air units that are ensnared can be attacked as though they were land units.
Causes a target enemy unit to be bound to the ground so that it cannot move for <A07J,Dur2> seconds. Air units that are ensnared can be attacked as though they were land units.
